OL,3,CResearch finds 'Man's Best Friend'
OL,4,Cexisted more than 14,000 years ago
OL,6,FAnimal remains discovered in a
OL,7,FSomerset cave shows dogs were being
OL,8,Fkept as domestic pets more than
OL,9,Ffourteen thousand years ago - the
OL,10,Fearliest known domesticated dog in the
OL,11,FUK.
OL,13,FExtensive research on the dog jawbone
OL,14,Fdiscovered in Cheddar shows it wasn't
OL,15,Fa wild animal but lived alongside
OL,16,Fhuman beings.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
