OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1774530670
OL,3,CResearch finds 'Man's Best Friend'
OL,4,Cexisted more than 14,000 years ago
OL,6,F"The dog jawbone from Gough's Cave
OL,7,Fthat has been identified as the
OL,8,Fearliest known domesticated dog in the
OL,9,FUK was among many specimens discovered
OL,10,Fduring the excavations in Gough's Cave
OL,11,Fbetween 1927 and 1931 was donated to
OL,12,Fthe Natural History Museum in 1928 by
OL,13,Fmy great-grandfather, Thomas Thynne,
OL,14,F5th Marquess of Bath.
OL,16,F"The paper is an exciting step in
OL,17,Flearning more about the history of the
OL,18,Fcaves and the part they played in the
OL,19,Flives of our ancestors."
OL,26,@nD@AOU{D@XO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
